OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable cloud around Tuesday
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells, the best of these
OL,7,Fmost likely during the afternoon.
OL,8,FWinds generally light with low cloud
OL,9,Fdeveloping in the south during the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBecoming cloudy overnight as
OL,13,Flow cloud and fog develops in the east
OL,14,Fof the region before spreading
OL,15,Fwestwards. Winds remain light.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FWednesday sees low cloud
OL,18,Fand fog slowly lifting and clearing
OL,19,Fduring the morning, with some brighter
OL,20,Fspells developing later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
