OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells expected Thursday before
OL,7,Fevening rain. Rain clears Friday
OL,8,Fmorning, leaving further sunny spells.
OL,9,FSaturday turns cloudy with rain and
OL,10,Fdrizzle.
